#DEITY
Filename		../deity/lolth~
Name		Lolth~
Description	Lolth, Demon Queen of Spiders
 
Domains  Spiders, Drow, Chaos, Evil       Alignment  Evil
 
The Demoness Lolth is a very powerful and feared Demon Lord. She
usually takes the form of a giant spider. Lolth enjoys to watch her
followers fight for her favor and despises all surface dwelling elves.
She is rumored to be the creator of the Drow race. Only female Drows
may worship her and gain her favor.
 
Favored Race  Drow           Hated Race  Elf
 
